\id 3JN - Bunama NT [bdd] -Papua New Guinea 1991 (DBL -2014) 
\h 3 Yoni 
\toc1 Yoni ꞌina lele hetoina 
\toc2 3 Yoni 
\toc3 3Yo 
\mt1 3 YONI  
\mt2 Yoni ꞌina lele hetoina  
\ip Yoni ꞌina leta bewa ꞌalona ꞌiheꞌoteꞌotetela mumuga bwebweꞌana weyahina.  
\c 1  
\s1 Loyauwedo  
\p
\v 1 Taugu ꞌimi bada, leta bewa yaleleyawa ꞌowa ꞌiyagu Geyo ꞌoiuwa. Moisa, ꞌateguwega yahelauwegowa.   
\p
\v 2 Ciyagu, ꞌigu ꞌahwanoi Yehoba ꞌoina wahiu ꞌina miya bwebweꞌana weyahina, yasanapuya weyahina yaluyaluwau ꞌina miya bwebweꞌana, eema maꞌina yaliyaya.  
\v 3 Mwalo tupwadi tasidao sitauyama ꞌebwa, ta ꞌino mumuga dumwaluna tetelina ꞌoinega sigihe yaliyayaegauwa, weyahina ꞌeda dumwaluna ꞌoinega ꞌutautauya.   
\p
\v 4 Bewa ꞌigu ꞌebe yaliyaya madouna ꞌeguma natugwao wasadi yahesagohe ꞌabehega ꞌeda dumwadumwaluna ꞌoinega sitautauya.   
\s1 Cada tolemao ma ꞌada ꞌalehao weyahidi  
\p
\v 5 Ciyagu, ꞌino lema eema ꞌino paihowa tasidao ma taumanao ꞌoidiya, tutaina ꞌeguma ꞌino ꞌasa sihapwesawa, weyahina yayaliyaya.  
\v 6 Ma tasidaowedi ꞌeguma sihilama ꞌino helau ꞌoidiya weyahina sihehepwaila tohekalesiyao ꞌoima. Moisa tuwa, taudi Yehoba ꞌina topaihowao, ꞌoinega ꞌilobwaineya ꞌeguma siꞌebeꞌebesinegomi nimaꞌabiyadi wete waꞌebwaedi.  
\v 7 Taudi Keliso ꞌina paihowa weyahina sisakosakowasi, ma lema geya sida lobeya taudi geya Yehoba ꞌana tohemisao ꞌoidiyega.  
\v 8 Coinega ꞌilobwainegita ma tauda talemedi, eema taudi mahetedao tahetopaihowa mahemahetena ꞌeda dumwadumwaluna weyahina.   
\p
\v 9 Cami hemataluwa yaꞌetoladi pwaiyawa, ꞌomi tohekalesiyao, ma loheyaina sanina Diotilipi nuwanuwana ma taunamo ꞌida loina, ꞌoinega taugu ꞌigu loina ꞌiꞌausiya,  
\v 10 ma ꞌigwae hesihesinuwegauwa, ma wete ꞌiyadao ꞌilososomanediya, ma ꞌeguma tupwadi ꞌoimiyega nuwanuwadi ma silemedi ꞌiꞌausidi, ma tohekalesiyaowedi ꞌipaꞌipaꞌidi. Coinega ꞌeguma ꞌabwa yalatuwa beno ꞌina mumugaedi yahegwaegwae weyahidi.   
\p
\v 11 Ciyagu, geyaꞌabwa mumuga galana ꞌumulimuliye, ma mumuga ꞌausalana hesi. Tobwebweꞌanao taudi Yehoba ꞌina bodao, ma topuiyao geya Yehoba sida sanapuya.   
\p
\v 12 Ma Dimitilo tauna loheya bwebweꞌana. Tomota mabwaiyadi ꞌidi hepwaila gidemusa, weyahina taudi heꞌita moisa ꞌana tomuliyao sihehepwaila ꞌabehega Dimitilo loheya bwebweꞌana, ma taugu wete ꞌigu hepwaila gidemusa, ma ꞌigu hepwaila wasanapuya ꞌabehega gwae moisa.   
\s1 Gwae ꞌana ꞌebelosaloha  
\p
\v 13 Nuwatuhu baibaiwadi simiyamiya ma nuwanuwagu yaleleyawa weyahidi,  
\v 14 ma tuwa, weyahina yanuwatuhu yahiya ꞌabehega ꞌabwa yatauyawa ma ꞌowa mahetegu tahegwaegwae.   
\p
\v 15 Yauwedo ꞌowa. Ciyadao ꞌebwa ꞌidi helau ꞌoiuwa. Ma ꞌiyadao nobwa sanidi ꞌaigeda ꞌaigeda wete ꞌoidiya ꞌigu helau ꞌuhepwaile.   